snippet.title: BlockWorld Ai // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3010030/BlockWorld_Ai/

RPG puzzle game in which players train a mysterious AI, Hoshihabito-kun, who learns how to move puzzles and the results, and fight powerful bosses together with players

Developed by One Team.
